 but the picture is kind of strange, as if it is somehow not alive or something ... 

00:02:31.986 --> 00:02:33.980
 Like some kind of dead photo. 

00:02:34.280 --> 00:02:36.026
 Take a closer look: 

00:02:36.093 --> 00:02:41.400
 Perhaps in this picture there is simply no color lighting and additional shades in the shadows. 

